text: The Parliament of the Cayman Islands is the unicameral legislature of the British Overseas Territory of the Cayman Islands. It is made up of 21 members; 19 elected members for a four-year term and two members ex officio.The Nineteen Single Member Electoral Districts Boundaries Order, 2015 ==References== Category:Cayman Islands Cayman Islands Category:Unicameral legislatures
title: Parliament of the Cayman Islands
